importance of their new modes

00:04:13.920 --> 00:04:16.140
or story that you
introduce to the game.

00:04:16.140 --> 00:04:17.790
They can also emphasize
the importance

00:04:17.790 --> 00:04:21.450
of new characters, story, or
skills, or new game mechanics

00:04:21.450 --> 00:04:22.680
that you have.

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:23.520
Targeted?

00:04:23.520 --> 00:04:26.720
They are more bound
to player groups.

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:30.510
They depend on
seasons, on regions.

00:04:30.510 --> 00:04:33.090
They also depend on
the progress sometimes

00:04:33.090 --> 00:04:34.930
the players have
made in the game.

