operations for local markets

00:04:51.330 --> 00:04:54.360
you need to make sure that you
think globally because even

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:59.080
the most famous events that
we are all used to celebrate

00:04:59.080 --> 00:05:04.530
might occur at different
times of the year

00:05:04.530 --> 00:05:05.580
in different countries.

00:05:05.580 --> 00:05:08.160
If we take the example
of Easter, or like when

00:05:08.160 --> 00:05:12.430
the Christmas is
celebrated in Russia,

00:05:12.430 --> 00:05:15.070
and they might not be
celebrated in the same way.

00:05:15.070 --> 00:05:16.820
So here you have
to be quite smart

00:05:16.820 --> 00:05:20.450
and, again, think globally.

